    {
      "number": 22,
      "id": "PR_kwDOKsv6Xc7kxru8",
      "title": "Address multile issues on encryption, reuse guard, and IANA",
      "url": "https://github.com/mlswg/mls-virtual-clients/pull/22",
      "state": "OPEN",
      "author": "kkohbrok",
      "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
      "assignees": [],
      "labels": [],
      "body": "- Derive AEAD key and nonce for DerivationInfo encryption from epoch_encryption_key with the LeafNode's encryption_key as context, making each key-nonce pair unique per operation\r\n- Restrict NewEmulatorClientState to Welcome-encrypted GroupInfo\r\n- Define N_e as the ratchet tree's leaf count including blank leaves\r\n- Fully instantiate FF1 (radix, numeral encoding, tweak, byte order)\r\n- Unify the three component registrations into a single virtual_clients component (Where: GI, LN, AD, ES) that also resolves the SafeExportSecret component ID; rename DerivationInfoComponent struct to DerivationInfo\r\n- Consolidate duplicate new-emulator sending restriction; note that rotation cannot be done by the new client in PrivateMessage-only groups\r\n- Replace Security and Privacy Considerations TODOs with initial text\r\n- Editorial fixes (resync wording, key_package_info reference, typos)",
      "createdAt": "2026-06-10T09:26:11Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-10T09:26:11Z",
